information: The company HARALD NEUHAUS GMBH FLEISCH & WURSTWAREN FABRIK, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1984, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Fish, Meat, Offal, and Meats, cooked and cured industries. It is based in Schwalbach, Germany.
